<h1>Users profile page</h1>

<p>***picture here maybe?</p>
<p><%= @user.first_name %> <%= @user.last_name %></p>
<p><%= @user.email %></p>

<h2>Your produce:</h2>
<ul>
  <% @user_items.each do |item| %>
    <li><%= link_to item.name, item_path(item) %></li>
  <% end %>
</ul>

<h2>Your bookings:</h2>
<ul>
  <% @user_bookings.each do |booking| %>
    <li><%= booking.date %></li>
    <li><%= link_to booking.seller.first_name, user_path(booking.seller) %></li>
    <li>if link above, which is suppose to be the user first_name, is something like /users/1, then that means that the user didnt set a first name</li>
  <% end %>
</ul>

